別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-Ph%E1%BB%A5c-C%E1%BB%95/Thanh-minh-c%E1%BA%A3m-th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-o4GCUia4svl4kcq5PpmFdw">Thanh minh cảm thương - 清明感傷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%9Bi-Ph%E1%BB%A5c-C%E1%BB%95/author-fmo28PNwjKb5s2uj6R9_ZA">Đới Phục Cổ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thi%E1%BB%81n-am-t%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BB%B1u/poem-wVwEZsJUGtPVUMf_6981dw">Thiền am tự cựu - 禪庵寺舊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BB%95/T%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-d8-MWLlAz2mQA8HWhlaasw">Tức sự - 即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C3%A1i-T%E1%BB%95/author-1RfRsGNVNQbtjX629ZNHvQ">Lý Thái Tổ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Giang-Nam-Si%C3%AAu-Nhi%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A0i-t%C3%A1c/poem-CbQ_atazJTAfWek56YDOeg">Vọng Giang Nam - Siêu Nhiên đài tác - 望江南－超然臺作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br></div>	</div>
